{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab These scripts move all or selected events from CC X to CC Y in one or multiple items.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab In the arrange view (item view), selected events are not taken into account, because you can't see what is selected.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab In the inline editor, you MUST hover the mouse over the active inline editor, otherwise ALL events will be affected, instead of only the selected ones.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab When hovering an inline editor, only the take under the mouse cursor will be affected, regardles of the item selection.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab You can easily customize the values in the scripts.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab The scripts work in the MIDI editor, inline editor and arrange view.\sa180\par}
}

